# LangGraph Adapter

Use when evaluating or integrating LangGraph for app-level agent workflows.

## References

- `langchain-ai/langgraph`: durable/stateful orchestration reference.

## Rules

- Keep LangGraph optional; core skills and compiler must not import it.
- Define state schemas, persistence, retries, and human approval nodes explicitly.
- Gate external tools and model calls by policy.
- Add tests around graph transitions and failure behavior before production use.

